TopicTitle: Waiter, theres a _____________ in my soup!

Articles.Content:
Soup-ception

Waiter, my signature's youtube video is playing, using my soup as its screen!

It happen all the time, don't pay too much attention to It.

Waiter there's a:

" Ten Timed Tamers Tamming Tim Self "

" Must flow like the Tames as a Timer to It.Self"

in my soup.

Arrgh. That's an atrocious annoying alliteration soup.

Waiter! There's a waiter in my soup!

Off course, it fall from the mountain source.

Waiter, there's something obvious in my soup.

DUH!

Waiter, the video in my signature is in my soup!

Well, that's the mud soup.

Waiter! There's a sun in my soup! He's enjoying the mud too much.

Sure but, what if on low ping hours you tube tend to do some looping ?

Waiter there's a loop pool breaker without pole in my soup.

Ah, yes sir. That would be the chef's, sir. He, erm, likes to ensure the flavors are all securely attached to the soup so they don't...get lost. Yes, sir, he does like to do so with considerable prejudice. I shall be right back in a moment, sir.

No, it's a Hypollo!
